er.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_external_dependency_involvement\",\"name\":\"Sign server and build storage involvement not confirmed or excluded\",\"description\":\"Available data did not show sign server or build storage failure, but direct step logs are required to confirm or exclude their involvement in the BBS_PackMake failure.\"}],\"preventive_actions\":[{\"id\":\"pa_memory_alerting\",\"name\":\"Implement memory utilization alerting on CRM build agents\",\"description\":\"Create alerts for CRMBuildsLinux-Ubuntu20-04 pool agents when memory utilization remains above 80% for more than 5 minutes.\"},{\"id\":\"pa_local_mnt_disk_alerting\",\"name\":\"Implement /local/mnt disk space alerting\",\"description\":\"Create alerts when /local/mnt free space drops below 200 GB, especially for crm-ubuntu232 because it has a documented prior space issue.\"},{\"id\":\"pa_docker_health_precheck\",\"name\":\"Add Docker health checks before BBS_PackMake\",\"description\":\"Add a lightweight pre-flight step before BBS_PackMake to verify Docker daemon health and available disk and memory.\"},{\"id\":\"pa_resource_aware_scheduling\",\"name\":\"Review concurrent step scheduling policy\",\"description\":\"Review crm-ubuntu232 stepLimit and resource-aware scheduling to reduce memory contention from concurrent jobs.\"},{\"id\":\"pa_docker_cache_cleanup\",\"name\":\"Schedule Docker image cache cleanup\",\"description\":\"Establish regular docker system prune or equivalent cleanup on CRM build agents to prevent Docker image/cache accumulation on local storage.\"},{\"id\":\"pa_track_agent_resource_history\",\"name\":\"Document and track crm-ubuntu232 resource history\",\"description\":\"Track the host's prior space issue annotation and perform formal health review before returning hosts with recurring resource issues to the production pool.\"}],\"remediations\":[{\"id\":\"rem_retrieve_step_log\",\"name\":\"Retrieve and examine BBS_PackMake step log\",\"description\":\"Retrieve BBS_PackMake.f1791bdd-1