el_602829\",\"target_id\":\"sym_abort_job_policy\"},{\"id\":\"rel_agent_has_mem_symptom\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"crm-ubuntu232 status is associated with observed memory growth.\",\"source_id\":\"status_agent_crm_ubuntu232\",\"target_id\":\"sym_memory_growth\"},{\"id\":\"rel_agent_has_cpu_symptom\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"crm-ubuntu232 status is associated with elevated kernel/system CPU.\",\"source_id\":\"status_agent_crm_ubuntu232\",\"target_id\":\"sym_elevated_kernel_cpu\"},{\"id\":\"rel_agent_has_disk_symptom\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"crm-ubuntu232 status is associated with /local/mnt free-space decline.\",\"source_id\":\"status_agent_crm_ubuntu232\",\"target_id\":\"sym_local_mnt_disk_decline\"},{\"id\":\"rel_agent_has_prior_space\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"crm-ubuntu232 status is associated with prior space issue annotation.\",\"source_id\":\"status_agent_crm_ubuntu232\",\"target_id\":\"sym_prior_space_issue_annotation\"},{\"id\":\"rel_agent_has_concurrent_job\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"crm-ubuntu232 had a concurrent job running during the failure window.\",\"source_id\":\"status_agent_crm_ubuntu232\",\"target_id\":\"sym_concurrent_job_same_agent\"},{\"id\":\"rel_exit_indicates_rc\",\"name\":\"indicates\",\"description\":\"Exit code 125 in the Docker-context workflow indicates the probable Docker container creation failure root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"sym_exit_code_125\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_failedreason_indicates_rc\",\"name\":\"indicates\",\"description\":\"failedReason=PostPackBBS indicates the failure occurred during the phase identified in the probable root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"sym_failed_reason_postpackbbs\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_short_duration_indicates_rc\",\"name\":\"indicates\",\"description\":\"Short step duration supports the container-startup failure assessment.\",\"source_id\":\"sym_short_step_duration\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_mem_indicates_rc\",\"name\":\"indicates\",\"description\":\"Memory pressure was correlated with and may support the probable Docker container creation failure root cause, but it was not directly proven.\",\"source_id\":\"sym_memory_growth\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_cpu_indicates_rc\",\"name\":\"indicates\",\"description\":\"Elevated kernel/system CPU was correlated with and may support the probable Docker container creation failure root cause, but it was not directly proven.\",\"source_id\":\"sym_elevated_kernel_cpu\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_step_log_gap_limits_rc\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"The missing BBS_PackMake step log limits confirmation of the exact sub-cause.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_bbs_packmake_step_log\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_docker_gap_limits_rc\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"Unknown Docker daemon state limits confirmation of the exact Docker sub-cause.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_docker_daemon_state\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_datadog_gap_limits_rc\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"No Datadog host logs limits host-side confirmation for the failure window.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_datadog_agent_logs\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_ext_gap_limits_rc\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"Unconfirmed external dependency involvement limits exclusion of non-Docker sub-causes without step logs.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_external_dependency_involvement\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rem_log_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses_gap\",\"description\":\"Retrieving the BBS_PackMake step log addresses the missing step log gap.\",\"source_id\":\"rem_retrieve_step_log\",\"target_id\":\"gap_bbs_packmake_step_log\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rem_docker_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses_gap\",\"description\":\"Checking Docker daemon logs addresses the Docker daemon state gap.\",\"source_id\":\"rem_check_docker_daemon_logs\",\"target_id\":\"gap_docker_daemon_state\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rem_mem_remediates_rc\",\"name\":\"remediates\",\"description\":\"Addressing memory pressure remediates a correlated resource condition for the probable root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"rem_address_memory_pressure\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rem_disk_remediates_rc\",\"name\":\"remediates\",\"description\":\"Investigating /local/mnt disk and Docker cache remediates a correlated resource condition for the probable root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"rem_investigate_local_mnt_disk\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rem_retry_after_rc\",\"name\":\"remediates\",\"description\":\"Retrying after agent health confirmation is a remediation step following investigation of the probable root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"rem_retry_after_health_check\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_pa_memory_prevents_rc\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"Memory alerting helps prevent recurrence of resource-pressure-related Docker container creation failures.\",\"source_id\":\"pa_memory_alerting\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_pa_disk_prevents_rc\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"/local/mnt disk alerting helps prevent recurrence of storage-pressure-related Docker container creation failures.\",\"source_id\":\"pa_local_mnt_disk_alerting\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_pa_docker_prevents_rc\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"Docker pre-flight health checks help prevent or catch Docker runtime failures before BBS_PackMake.\",\"source_id\":\"pa_docker_health_precheck\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_pa_sched_prevents_rc\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"Resource-aware scheduling helps prevent concurrent workload pressure on crm-ubuntu232.\",\"source_id\":\"pa_resource_aware_scheduling\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_pa_cleanup_prevents_rc\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"Docker cache cleanup helps prevent local storage accumulation contributing to Docker failures.\",\"source_id\":\"pa_docker_cache_cleanup\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_pa_history_prevents_rc\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"Tracking resource history helps prevent recurrence on hosts with known resource issues.\",\"source_id\":\"pa_track_agent_resource_history\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_conf_annotates_rc\",\"name\":\"annotates\",\"description\":\"Confidence annotation applies to the probable root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"ann_confidence_medium\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_infra_annotates_rc\",\"name\":\"annotates\",\"description\":\"Infrastructure-not-code assessment applies to the probable root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"ann_infrastructure_not_code\",\"target_id\":\"rc_docker_container_creation_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_job_status_proc\",\"name\":\"has_status\",\"description\":\"The procedure/job ended with error and ABORT status.\",\"source_id\":\"proc_build_container_rel_602829\",\"target_id\":\"status_job_error_abort\"},{\"id\":\"rel_agent_status_proc\",\"name\":\"has_status\",\"description\":\"The procedure/job ran on agent crm-ubuntu232.\",\"source_id\":\"proc_build_container_rel_602829\",\"target_id\":\"status_agent_crm_ubuntu232\"},{\"id\":\"rel_commander_status_proc\",\"name\":\"has_status\",\"description\":\"Commander node status was assessed for the procedure/job and found not contributing.\",\"source_id\":\"proc_build_container_rel_602829\",\"target_id\":\"status_commander_normal\"}]}",
    "embedding_text": "Log symptoms:  [{'id': 'sym_exit_code_125', 'name': 'BBS_PackMake exit code 125', 'description': 'FinishCommandOperation at 09:44:05.422Z, RunCommandCallback at 09:44:05.430Z, and CommitCommandResultsOperation at 09:44:05.441Z recorded exit code 125 for BBS_PackMake.'}, {'id': 'sym_failed_reason_postpackbbs', 'name': 'failedReason=PostPackBBS', 'description': 'BuildInfoJson property written at 2026-07-06T09:46:42.241Z recorded failedReason=PostPackBBS and buildStatus=Failed.'}, {'id': 'sym_abort_job_policy', 'name': 'abortJob policy triggered', 'description': 'CheckAbortCondition at 09:44:05.483Z evaluated errorHandling=abortJob for the failed BBS_PackMake step and triggered AbortJobOperation at 09:44:05.517Z.'}, {'id': 'sym_short_step_duration', 'name': 'BBS_PackMake failed after about 30 seconds', 'description': 'BBS_PackMake ran from 09:43:34.974Z to 09:44:05.441Z, which the RCA assessed as consistent with container startup failure rather than a compile/link failure.'}, {'id': 'sym_memory_growth', 'name': 'Agent memory utilization rose to about 85%', 'description': 'Datadog metrics showed crm-ubuntu232 memory used rose from about 186.8 GB, about 74%, to about 228-229 GB, about 85%, by 09:44Z, an increase of about 42 GB.'}, {'id': 'sym_elevated_kernel_cpu', 'name': 'Elevated kernel/system CPU', 'description': 'Datadog metrics showed cpu_sys peaked at average 12.60%, max 14.35%, and exceeded cpu_user during 09:28-09:39, indicating heavy kernel/I/O/syscall activity.'}, {'id': 'sym_local_mnt_disk_decline', 'name': '/local/mnt free space declined', 'description': 'Datadog metrics showed /local/mnt free space declined by about 31 GB, from about 919 GB to 888 GB over 47 minutes; it was not full in the observed data.'}, {'id': 'sym_prior_space_issue_annotation', 'name': 'Prior space issue annotation on crm-ubuntu232', 'description': 'The CloudBees resource description for crm-ubuntu232 contained the historical note: \"syelugub- 7/31 space issue 7/17 smanley - put back in service\".'}, {'id': 'sym_concurrent_job_same_agent', 'name': 'Concurrent job on same agent', 'description': 'Concurrent job f1791f06-4a84-f1fa-9190-1ea035bf3243 was running VerifySrc and Make on crm-ubuntu232 at the time of failure.'}, {'id': 'sym_nonfatal_nosuchproperty', 'name': 'Non-fatal NoSuchProperty events', 'description': 'NoSuchProperty events for customType and report-urls occurred during or after finalization, and the RCA explicitly assessed them as not related to the failure.'}]\n    \n Root Causes:  [{'id': 'rc_docker_container_creation_failure', 'name': 'Probable Docker container creation failure during PostPackBBS', 'description': 'The RCA identified the most probable root cause as Docker container creation/run failure during the BBS_PackMake/PostPackBBS phase. Evidence included exit code 125 in an ONPREMCONTAINERIZED workflow, BuildInfoJson.failedReason=PostPackBBS, short 30-second step duration, agent memory growth to about 85%, elevated kernel CPU, concurrent job load, and prior resource-space history on crm-ubuntu232. Confidence was MEDIUM because the direct step execution log was unavailable.'}]\n    \n Data Gaps:  [{'id': 'gap_bbs_packmake_step_log', 'name': 'Missing BBS_PackMake step execution log', 'description': 'BBS_PackMake.f1791bdd-17fb-f111-93af-4efb9ff91010.log from crm-ubuntu232 was not available in Splunk or Datadog. This log is required to confirm the exact Docker error message and precise sub-cause.'}, {'id': 'gap_docker_daemon_state', 'name': 'Docker daemon state unknown at failure time', 'description': 'The RCA did not have docker daemon logs or host journal evidence from crm-ubuntu232 around 09:43:34Z-09:44:05Z, so it could not confirm OOM, storage-driver, image-pull, or other Docker daemon errors.'}, {'id': 'gap_datadog_agent_logs', 'name': 'No Datadog logs for crm-ubuntu232 in failure window', 'description': 'Datadog Logs query for 09:43:00Z-09:44:30Z returned 0 results for crm-ubuntu232 in the flex tier.'}, {'id': 'gap_external_dependency_involvement', 'name': 'Sign server and build storage involvement not confirmed or excluded', 'description': 'Available data did not show sign server or build storage failure, but direct step logs are required to confirm or exclude their involvement in the BBS_PackMake failure.'}]",
