    "file_name": "RCA_f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243.txt",
    "log_text": "Root Cause Analysis Report\nJob ID: f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243  |  Build: CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1  |  Outcome: ERROR\n\n---\n1. Executive Summary\nCloudBees job f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243 failed during the \"Make\" step with exit code 4 on agent host crm-ubuntu322. The CloudBees execution context explicitly classifies the failure reason as \"Compile\". The Make step ran for approximately 2 minutes 25 seconds (06:19:34 \u2192 06:21:59 UTC) before terminating with a non-zero exit code.\n\nCritical Finding: Agent host crm-ubuntu322 has no Datadog telemetry coverage \u2014 it is absent from the Datadog host inventory, has no registered Datadog Agent, and produced zero logs, metrics, or events in any monitored data source. Root cause cannot be confirmed from monitoring data alone. The CloudBees step execution logs on the agent must be examined directly.\n\nAll other \"compile error\" and \"commander error\" log entries found during the correlation window belong to unrelated systems (Gerrit GC operations, GitHub Actions runners) and are explicitly excluded per scope rules.\n\n---\n2. Job Context\nJob ID: f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243\nJob Name: CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1_20260706_231829_231836\nProject: CRMBuilds\nProcedure: Build.Rel.602829\nOutcome: completed_error / error\nFailed Step: Make (Step ID: f179cbb0-4c2c-f151-ab07-4efb9ff91010)\nExit Code: 4\nAgent Host: crm-ubuntu322\nBuild Name: CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1\nDeclared Failure Reason: Compile\n---\n3. Build Timeline\nTime (UTC)\tEvent\tDetail\n2026-07-07 06:18:36\tJob Started\tCRMBuilds / Build.Rel.602829 initiated\n2026-07-07 06:19:34\tMake Step Started\tStep begins on crm-ubuntu322 \u2014 Correlation Window Opens\n2026-07-07 06:21:59\tMake Step FAILED\tExit Code 4 \u2014 Correlation Window Closes (duration: ~2m 25s)\n2026-07-07 06:24:16\tJob Ended\tJob terminates with outcome: error\n---\n4. Execution Path Inventory\nFailed Step: \"Make\" \u2014 compile/build step invoking make toolchain\nAgent Host: crm-ubuntu322 (Linux Ubuntu \u2014 inferred from hostname pattern)\nCommander Host: Not identified \u2014 no evidence of Commander contribution to failure\nInvoked Services: Source code repository (SCM) and build toolchain (make) \u2014 specific URLs/endpoints not available from metadata\n---\n5. Detected Error Codes\nCode\tSource\tMeaning\tEvidence\nExit Code 4\tCloudBees Step Metadata\tGNU Make exit code 4 = build error (compilation failure, missing target, or fatal make error). Distinct from exit code 2 (usage error) or 1 (rule failure).\tProvided in job payload \u2014 failedStep.exitCode = \"4\"\nCompile\tCloudBees executionContext\tBuild system explicitly classified failure as a compile-type failure\texecutionContext.failedReason = \"Compile\"\n---\n6. Correlated Observations\nCloudBees\nJob metadata confirms: step \"Make\" failed with exit code 4 on host crm-ubuntu322\nFailure reason explicitly set to \"Compile\" in execution context\nStep duration: ~2 minutes 25 seconds \u2014 consistent with a partial compile run before failure\nBuild name: CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1 \u2014 PERF.INT build type (performance integration)\nConfidence: HIGH \u2014 directly from job payload\nAgent Host (crm-ubuntu322)\n\u26a0\ufe0f Agent host crm-ubuntu322 has NO telemetry coverage in Datadog.\nThe host is absent from the Datadog host inventory. No CPU, memory, disk, or network metrics were returned. No logs were found. No Datadog Agent appears to be installed or reporting from this host.\n\nRoot cause cannot be determined from monitoring data. CloudBees step execution logs must be examined directly on crm-ubuntu322.\n\nOther CRM Ubuntu agents (crm-ubuntu265, crm-ubuntu238) are registered in Datadog with Agent 7.64.1 \u2014 confirming the CRM fleet does use Datadog, but crm-ubuntu322 is not enrolled\nReference metrics on crm-ubuntu238 showed a CPU spike to ~24.7% at the end of the window \u2014 this is on a different host and is OUT_OF_SCOPE\nReference metrics on crm-ubuntu265 showed stable low CPU (~0.03\u20130.24%) \u2014 OUT_OF_SCOPE\nCommander Host\nNo Commander host identified in job metadata\nNo Commander-related errors found in logs during the correlation window\nNo evidence of Commander contribution to failure \u2014 OUT_OF_SCOPE\nDatadog\nZero log entries matching job ID, build name, procedure name, or agent hostname\nZero Datadog events for crm-ubuntu322\nZero active incidents during the job execution window\nZero monitors configured for crm-ubuntu322\nFinding: No Datadog coverage for the failed agent host\nSplunk\nNot queried in this investigation (Datadog flex tier searched as primary log source)\nSplunk ecommander index may contain CloudBees step logs \u2014 recommended as next step\nExternal Dependencies \u2014 SCOPE VALIDATION\nGerrit GC errors (e.g., fatal: bad object refs/changes/01/220101/1 on qctaisw_tools/hexagon-sdk-6.2.0-win.git) \u2014 found at 06:24:06 UTC, after the failed step ended at 06:21:59 UTC. OUT_OF_SCOPE \u2014 no direct link to the Make step, and occurred after failure.\nGitHub Actions runner log (ci-foundry, Yocto build) \u2014 unrelated CI system, different job ID, different runner. OUT_OF_SCOPE\nGerrit CD sanity checker error (missing cd.xml) \u2014 unrelated Android_Main project. OUT_OF_SCOPE\n---\n7. Probable Root Cause\nPrimary: Compile Failure during Make step on crm-ubuntu322\n\nThe CloudBees execution context explicitly classifies the failure as \"Compile\". GNU Make exit code 4 indicates a fatal build error \u2014 typically a compiler error, missing source file, missing symbol, or unresolvable dependency that caused make to abort. The step ran for ~2m 25s before failing, consistent with a partial compile run that encountered a fatal error mid-build.\n\nSupporting Evidence:\n\nexitCode = 4 (GNU Make fatal error) \u2014 from CloudBees job payload\nfailedReason = \"Compile\" \u2014 from CloudBees executionContext\nStep name = \"Make\" \u2014 direct invocation of the make build system\nBuild type = PERF.INT (performance integration) \u2014 may involve specialized compiler flags or toolchains\nCannot confirm specific compile error (missing symbol, syntax error, toolchain issue, missing dependency) without direct access to the Make step's stdout/stderr logs on crm-ubuntu322.\n\n---\n8. Confidence Level\n\u26a0\ufe0f MEDIUM\n\nThe failure category (Compile) is confirmed with HIGH confidence from CloudBees metadata\nThe specific compile error (root file, line, symbol) is UNKNOWN \u2014 no step logs available in any monitored system\nAgent host has zero telemetry coverage \u2014 infrastructure contribution (disk full, OOM, NFS mount failure) cannot be ruled out or confirmed\nOverall confidence is MEDIUM: category is clear, specific cause requires direct log access\n---\n9. Infrastructure vs Code Assessment\nAssessment\tVerdict\tReason\nInfrastructure Issue\tPOSSIBLE \u2014 UNCONFIRMED\tNo agent telemetry available. Cannot confirm or exclude disk exhaustion, OOM, or NFS issues on crm-ubuntu322.\nCode Issue\tLIKELY \u2014 YES\tCloudBees explicitly classifies as \"Compile\" failure. Exit code 4 from GNU Make is consistent with a compiler/build error in source code or build scripts.\nMixed\tPOSSIBLE\tCannot be excluded without agent-level evidence.\n---\n10. Recommended Remediation\nRetrieve Make step logs directly from crm-ubuntu322: Access the CloudBees agent workspace on crm-ubuntu322 and retrieve the stdout/stderr output of the \"Make\" step. Look for compiler error messages (e.g., error:, undefined reference, No rule to make target, fatal error).\nCheck CloudBees job log archive: Access the CloudBees Commander UI for job f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243 \u2192 Step \"Make\" \u2192 View Log to retrieve the full step output.\nIdentify the failing compilation unit: The Make exit code 4 typically appears after a compiler error. Identify the specific source file, module, or target that failed.\nCheck for recent code changes: Review recent commits to the source tree used by build CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1 (branch/tag associated with this PERF.INT build) for changes that may have introduced a compile error.\nVerify toolchain availability: Confirm that the compiler, linker, and all required build tools are present and correctly versioned on crm-ubuntu322.\nCheck disk space on crm-ubuntu322: Verify that the build workspace has sufficient disk space (Make exit code 4 can also occur if the compiler cannot write output files due to disk exhaustion).\n---\n11. Preventive Actions\nInstall Datadog Agent on crm-ubuntu322: This host has zero observability coverage. Install and configure the Datadog Agent to collect CPU, memory, disk, and process metrics. This is critical for future RCA investigations.\nEnable CloudBees log forwarding to Datadog/Splunk: Configure CloudBees agent step logs to be forwarded to a centralized log platform so that compile errors are searchable without direct host access.\nAdd disk space monitoring: Implement disk utilization alerts on all CRM build agents to detect disk exhaustion before it causes build failures.\nStandardize agent enrollment: Audit all CRM build agents against the Datadog host inventory. Several CRM Ubuntu agents are enrolled (crm-ubuntu265, crm-ubuntu238) but crm-ubuntu322 is not \u2014 ensure consistent coverage across the fleet.\nPre-build environment validation: Add a pre-step to the CloudBees procedure to validate toolchain availability, disk space, and required dependencies before invoking Make.\nJIRA tracking: A JIRA search for CQ2390 was active during the build window \u2014 ensure build failures are automatically linked to JIRA tickets for tracking and trend analysis.\n---\n12. Sources Used\nSource Type\tQuery Window\tEvidence\tRelevance\nCloudBees Job Payload\tN/A (provided)\tJob ID, step name, exit code 4, agent host, failure reason \"Compile\"\tHIGH \u2014 Primary evidence source\nDatadog Logs (Flex)\t06:18:00\u201306:25:00 UTC\tNo relevant findings for job ID, build name, agent host, or procedure\tSearched \u2014 no coverage for crm-ubuntu322\nDatadog Host Inventory\tCurrent\tcrm-ubuntu322 NOT present. 20 other CRM hosts found. crm-ubuntu265, crm-ubuntu238 confirmed with Agent 7.64.1\tHIGH \u2014 Confirms telemetry gap\nDatadog Metrics\t06:19:00\u201306:22:30 UTC\tNo metrics for crm-ubuntu322. Reference metrics retrieved for crm-ubuntu265 and crm-ubuntu238 (different hosts)\tNo relevant findings for failed host\nDatadog Events\t06:18:00\u201306:25:00 UTC\tNo events for crm-ubuntu322\tNo relevant findings\nDatadog Incidents\t06:00:00\u201306:25:00 UTC\tZero active incidents during job window\tNo relevant findings\nDatadog Monitors\tCurrent\tNo monitors configured for crm-ubuntu322\tConfirms monitoring gap\n",
    "log_json": "{\"log_record\":{\"id\":\"log_rca_f179cbb0_412f_f18b_a4a8_1ea035bf3243\",\"name\":\"RCA_f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243.txt\",\"description\":\"Root Cause Analysis report for CloudBees job f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243, build CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1, outcome ERROR.\"},\"procedures\":[{\"id\":\"proc_build_rel_602829\",\"name\":\"Build.Rel.602829\",\"description\":\"CloudBees procedure in project CRMBuilds for job f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243.\"}],\"steps\":[{\"id\":\"step_make_f179cbb0_4c2c_f151_ab07_4efb9ff91010\",\"name\":\"Make\",\"description\":\"Failed CloudBees step ID f179cbb0-4c2c-f151-ab07-4efb9ff91010. Ran on agent host crm-ubuntu322 from 2026-07-07 06:19:34 UTC to 06:21:59 UTC and failed with exit code 4 after approximately 2 minutes 25 seconds.\"}],\"step_classes\":[{\"id\":\"step_class_compile_build_make\",\"name\":\"Compile/build step invoking make\",\"description\":\"The failed step is described as a compile/build step invoking the make toolchain.\"}],\"log_symptoms\":[{\"id\":\"symptom_make_failed_exit_code_4\",\"name\":\"Make step failed with exit code 4\",\"description\":\"CloudBees step metadata reports failedStep.exitCode = \\\"4\\\" for the Make step.\"},{\"id\":\"symptom_declared_failure_reason_compile\",\"name\":\"Declared failure reason Compile\",\"description\":\"CloudBees execution context explicitly sets failedReason = \\\"Compile\\\".\"},{\"id\":\"symptom_job_completed_error\",\"name\":\"Job outcome completed_error / error\",\"description\":\"The job outcome is reported as completed_error / error and the job ended at 2026-07-07 06:24:16 UTC.\"},{\"id\":\"symptom_no_matching_datadog_logs\",\"name\":\"No matching Datadog logs\",\"description\":\"Datadog log searches returned zero log entries matching the job ID, build name, procedure name, or agent hostname.\"}],\"system_statuses\":[{\"id\":\"status_agent_no_datadog_coverage\",\"name\":\"crm-ubuntu322 has no Datadog telemetry coverage\",\"descripti