e specific compile error.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_no_datadog_coverage_agent\",\"name\":\"No Datadog coverage for failed agent\",\"description\":\"crm-ubuntu322 has no Datadog Agent registration, host inventory entry, logs, metrics, events, or monitors, preventing telemetry-based confirmation of root cause.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_specific_compile_error_unknown\",\"name\":\"Specific compile error unknown\",\"description\":\"The report cannot identify whether the Make failure was caused by a missing symbol, syntax error, toolchain issue, missing dependency, missing target, or other fatal build error.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_infrastructure_conditions_unknown\",\"name\":\"Infrastructure conditions on crm-ubuntu322 unknown\",\"description\":\"Because no agent telemetry is available, disk exhaustion, OOM, NFS mount failure, or related infrastructure issues cannot be confirmed or excluded.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_splunk_not_queried\",\"name\":\"Splunk not queried\",\"description\":\"Splunk was not queried in this investigation. The report notes that the Splunk ecommander index may contain CloudBees step logs.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_commander_host_not_identified\",\"name\":\"Commander host not identified\",\"description\":\"The Commander host was not identified in the job metadata.\"},{\"id\":\"gap_scm_endpoints_unavailable\",\"name\":\"SCM URLs or endpoints unavailable\",\"description\":\"The report states that invoked services include source code repository and build toolchain, but specific SCM URLs or endpoints are not available from metadata.\"}],\"preventive_actions\":[{\"id\":\"prev_install_datadog_agent_crm_ubuntu322\",\"name\":\"Install Datadog Agent on crm-ubuntu322\",\"description\":\"Install and configure the Datadog Agent on crm-ubuntu322 to collect CPU, memory, disk, and process metrics for future RCA investigations.\"},{\"id\":\"prev_enable_cloudbees_log_forwarding\",\"name\":\"Enable CloudBees log forwarding to Datadog or Splunk\",\"description\":\"Configure CloudBees agent step logs to be forwarded to a centralized log platform so compile errors are searchable without direct host access.\"},{\"id\":\"prev_add_disk_space_monitoring\",\"name\":\"Add disk space monitoring\",\"description\":\"Implement disk utilization alerts on all CRM build agents to detect disk exhaustion before it causes build failures.\"},{\"id\":\"prev_standardize_agent_enrollment\",\"name\":\"Standardize CRM build agent enrollment\",\"description\":\"Audit all CRM build agents against the Datadog host inventory and ensure consistent observability coverage across the fleet.\"},{\"id\":\"prev_prebuild_environment_validation\",\"name\":\"Pre-build environment validation\",\"description\":\"Add a pre-step to the CloudBees procedure to validate toolchain availability, disk space, and required dependencies before invoking Make.\"},{\"id\":\"prev_jira_failure_tracking\",\"name\":\"JIRA tracking for build failures\",\"description\":\"Ensure build failures are automatically linked to JIRA tickets for tracking and trend analysis.\"}],\"remediations\":[{\"id\":\"rem_retrieve_make_logs_from_agent\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Make step logs from crm-ubuntu322\",\"description\":\"Access the CloudBees agent workspace on crm-ubuntu322 and retrieve stdout/stderr output for the Make step, looking for compiler error messages such as error:, undefined reference, No rule to make target, or fatal error.\"},{\"id\":\"rem_check_cloudbees_job_log_archive\",\"name\":\"Check CloudBees job log archive\",\"description\":\"Use the CloudBees Commander UI for job f179cbb0-412f-f18b-a4a8-1ea035bf3243, Step \\\"Make\\\", View Log, to retrieve full step output.\"},{\"id\":\"rem_identify_failing_compilation_unit\",\"name\":\"Identify failing compilation unit\",\"description\":\"Use the Make output to identify the specific source file, module, or target that failed.\"},{\"id\":\"rem_review_recent_code_changes\",\"name\":\"Review recent code changes\",\"description\":\"Review recent commits to the source tree used by build CQ2390.LA.1.0-00317-PERF.INT-1 for changes that may have introduced a compile error.\"},{\"id\":\"rem_verify_toolchain_availability\",\"name\":\"Verify toolchain availability\",\"description\":\"Confirm that the compiler, linker, and required build tools are present and correctly versioned on crm-ubuntu322.\"},{\"id\":\"rem_check_disk_space_crm_ubuntu322\",\"name\":\"Check disk space on crm-ubuntu322\",\"description\":\"Verify that the build workspace on crm-ubuntu322 has sufficient disk space, since Make can fail if the compiler cannot write output files.\"}],\"annotations\":[{\"id\":\"ann_confidence_medium\",\"name\":\"Overall confidence MEDIUM\",\"description\":\"The report rates confidence as MEDIUM: the failure category Compile is confirmed from CloudBees metadata, but the specific compile error is unknown and agent telemetry is absent.\"},{\"id\":\"ann_failure_category_high_confidence\",\"name\":\"Failure category high confidence\",\"description\":\"The report states that the Compile failure category is confirmed with high confidence from CloudBees metadata.\"},{\"id\":\"ann_unrelated_errors_out_of_scope\",\"name\":\"Unrelated correlated errors excluded\",\"description\":\"Gerrit GC errors, GitHub Actions runner logs, and a Gerrit CD sanity checker error were found but explicitly marked OUT_OF_SCOPE because they involve unrelated systems, different jobs, or occurred after the failed step.\"},{\"id\":\"ann_primary_source_cloudbees_payload\",\"name\":\"CloudBees payload primary evidence\",\"description\":\"CloudBees job payload is identified as the primary evidence source for job ID, failed step, exit code 4, agent host, and failure reason Compile.\"}],\"relationships\":[{\"id\":\"rel_extracted_proc_build_rel\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Procedure extracted from source RCA log.\",\"source_id\":\"proc_build_rel_602829\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_f179cbb0_412f_f18b_a4a8_1ea035bf3243\"},{\"id\":\"rel_extracted_step_make\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\