    "embedding_text": "Log symptoms:  [{'id': 'symptom_make_failed_exit_code_4', 'name': 'Make step failed with exit code 4', 'description': 'CloudBees step metadata reports failedStep.exitCode = \"4\" for the Make step.'}, {'id': 'symptom_declared_failure_reason_compile', 'name': 'Declared failure reason Compile', 'description': 'CloudBees execution context explicitly sets failedReason = \"Compile\".'}, {'id': 'symptom_job_completed_error', 'name': 'Job outcome completed_error / error', 'description': 'The job outcome is reported as completed_error / error and the job ended at 2026-07-07 06:24:16 UTC.'}, {'id': 'symptom_no_matching_datadog_logs', 'name': 'No matching Datadog logs', 'description': 'Datadog log searches returned zero log entries matching the job ID, build name, procedure name, or agent hostname.'}]\n    \n Root Causes:  [{'id': 'root_cause_probable_compile_failure_make', 'name': 'Probable compile failure during Make step', 'description': 'The probable root cause is a compile failure during the Make step on crm-ubuntu322. Evidence includes CloudBees failedReason = \"Compile\", step name \"Make\", and exit code 4. The report states that the exact compiler error, file, line, symbol, target, or dependency cannot be confirmed without direct Make stdout/stderr logs.'}]\n    \n Data Gaps:  [{'id': 'gap_make_stdout_stderr_unavailable', 'name': 'Make step stdout/stderr unavailable', 'description': 'The CloudBees step execution logs from crm-ubuntu322 were not available in monitored data sources and must be examined directly to identify the specific compile error.'}, {'id': 'gap_no_datadog_coverage_agent', 'name': 'No Datadog coverage for failed agent', 'description': 'crm-ubuntu322 has no Datadog Agent registration, host inventory entry, logs, metrics, events, or monitors, preventing telemetry-based confirmation of root cause.'}, {'id': 'gap_specific_compile_error_unknown', 'name': 'Specific compile error unknown', 'description': 'The report cannot identify whether the Make failure was caused by a missing symbol, syntax error, toolchain issue, missing dependency, missing target, or other fatal build error.'}, {'id': 'gap_infrastructure_conditions_unknown', 'name': 'Infrastructure conditions on crm-ubuntu322 unknown', 'description': 'Because no agent telemetry is available, disk exhaustion, OOM, NFS mount failure, or related infrastructure issues cannot be confirmed or excluded.'}, {'id': 'gap_splunk_not_queried', 'name': 'Splunk not queried', 'description': 'Splunk was not queried in this investigation. The report notes that the Splunk ecommander index may contain CloudBees step logs.'}, {'id': 'gap_commander_host_not_identified', 'name': 'Commander host not identified', 'description': 'The Commander host was not identified in the job metadata.'}, {'id': 'gap_scm_endpoints_unavailable', 'name': 'SCM URLs or endpoints unavailable', 'description': 'The report states that invoked services include source code repository and build toolchain, but specific SCM URLs or endpoints are not available from metadata.'}]",
