acted_from\",\"description\":\"Overlapping execution remediation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"remediate_check_overlapping_execution\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remediate_rerun_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Rerun remediation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"remediate_rerun_wlan_tfh_jobs\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remediate_retry_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Retry logic remediation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"remediate_add_verifysrc_retry_logic\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remediate_logs_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Retrieving step logs addresses missing stdout/stderr and endpoint identification gaps.\",\"source_id\":\"remediate_retrieve_step_logs_and_identify_endpoint\",\"target_id\":\"gap_step_stdout_stderr_missing\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remediate_logs_addresses_endpoint_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Identifying the upload destination addresses the unknown remote endpoint gap.\",\"source_id\":\"remediate_retrieve_step_logs_and_identify_endpoint\",\"target_id\":\"gap_remote_upload_endpoint_unknown\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remediate_retry_addresses_root_cause\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Adding retry logic addresses the probable upload abort failure mode.\",\"source_id\":\"remediate_add_verifysrc_retry_logic\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_systemic_verifysrc_upload_abort\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_log_pipeline_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Datadog log pipeline preventive action extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_configure_datadog_log_pipeline\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_endpoint_monitor_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Endpoint monitoring preventive action extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_monitor_verifysrc_upload_endpoint\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_disk_monitor_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Disk monitoring preventive action extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_disk_usage_monitoring\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_cleanup_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Workspace cleanup preventive action extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_workspace_cleanup_policy\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_concurrency_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Concurrent job limit preventive action extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_concurrent_job_limit_review\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_timeout_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"VerifySrc timeout preventive action extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_verifysrc_timeout_increase\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_log_pipeline_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Configuring Datadog logs addresses missing host log forwarding.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_configure_datadog_log_pipeline\",\"target_id\":\"gap_step_stdout_stderr_missing\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_endpoint_monitor_addresses_root_cause\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Monitoring the upload endpoint addresses the likely endpoint-related failure mode.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_monitor_verifysrc_upload_endpoint\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_systemic_verifysrc_upload_abort\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prevent_timeout_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Increasing VerifySrc timeout addresses the possible insufficient-timeout mechanism.\",\"source_id\":\"prevent_verifysrc_timeout_increase\",\"target_id\":\"gap_script_behavior_unconfirmed\"},{\"id\":\"rel_annotation_job_context_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Job context annotation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"annotation_job_context\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_annotation_timeline_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Timeline annotation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"annotation_timeline\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_annotation_confidence_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Confidence annotation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"annotation_confidence\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_annotation_sources_extracted\",\"name\":\"extracted_from\",\"description\":\"Sources-used annotation extracted from source log.\",\"source_id\":\"annotation_sources_used\",\"target_id\":\"log_rca_179ca58_7a71_f11a_8dc3_4efb9ff91010\"}]}",
    "embedding_text": "Log symptoms:  [{'id': 'symptom_job_error_aborted', 'name': 'CloudBees job completed_error / error with Aborted classification', 'description': 'Job f179ca58-7a71-f11a-8dc3-4efb9ff91010 failed with outcome completed_error / error and CloudBees execution context failedReason Aborted.'}, {'id': 'symptom_verifysrc_exit_code_2', 'name': 'VerifySrc failed with exit code 2', 'description': 'CloudBees step metadata reports failedStep.exitCode = \"2\" for VerifySrc, interpreted in the RCA as a script-level abort.'}, {'id': 'symptom_large_inbound_prestep', 'name': 'Large inbound transfer before VerifySrc', 'description': 'Datadog metrics show approximately 148MB inbound during job setup around 2026-07-07 06:09:28Z to 06:11:05Z, described as a large source package download.'}, {'id': 'symptom_sustained_outbound_transfer', 'name': 'Sustained outbound transfer during and around VerifySrc', 'description': 'Datadog metrics show approximately 74MB total outbound transfer starting before VerifySrc and continuing through the step window, including pre-step and during-step system.net.bytes_sent bursts.'}, {'id': 'symptom_abort_during_outbound_transfer', 'name': 'VerifySrc aborted during outbound transfer window', 'description': 'VerifySrc started at 06:11:47Z while outbound transfer was already in progress and aborted at 06:12:46Z after sustained outbound activity during the step.'}, {'id': 'symptom_cross_job_pattern', 'name': 'Recurring WLAN TFH VerifySrc abort pattern', 'description': 'The RCA reports three WLAN TFH VerifySrc aborts with the same signatures: exit code 2, failed reason Aborted, procedure Build.Rel.602829, and large outbound transfers across jobs f179ca58, f179cb7a, and f179cb72 on two agents.'}, {'id': 'symptom_same_host_repeat', 'name': 'Same host repeated VerifySrc abort', 'description': 'Agent host san-w175-ha1-4-07 failed VerifySrc for this job and later job f179cb72 with identical signature on the same morning session.'}, {'id': 'symptom_disk_usage_jump_secondary', 'name': 'Disk usage jump after this job', 'description': \"Datadog metrics show disk usage on san-w175-ha1-4-07 was 5.13% at this job's step time and 42.1% during later job f179cb72, a reported increase of approximately 37% in about 8 minutes. The RCA treats this as a secondary risk, not the cause of this job's failure.\"}, {'id': 'symptom_overlapping_job_execution', 'name': 'Overlapping execution on same agent', 'description': 'Job f179cb72 reportedly started on san-w175-ha1-4-07 at 06:16:52Z while this job was still in teardown and before this job ended at 06:18:16Z.'}]\n    \n Root Causes:  [{'id': 'root_cause_systemic_verifysrc_upload_abort', 'name': 'Probable systemic VerifySrc upload abort: remote endpoint failure or script timeout', 'description': 'The RCA identifies the probable root cause as a systemic VerifySrc upload operation issue. A sustained outbound transfer of approximately 74MB began before VerifySrc formally started and continued during the step, after which VerifySrc aborted with exit code 2. The same pattern across multiple WLAN TFH jobs and two agents points to either an unavailable or slow remote upload endpoint, or a VerifySrc script timeout that is too short for the data volume. The exact trigger is not confirmed without step logs.'}]\n    \n Data Gaps:  [{'id': 'gap_step_stdout_stderr_missing', 'name': 'VerifySrc stdout/stderr not available in Datadog', 'description': 'No application-level logs are forwarded from san-w175-ha1-4-07 to Datadog. Step-level stdout/stderr must be retrieved directly from CloudBees to confirm the upload destination and exact abort message.'}, {'id': 'gap_remote_upload_endpoint_unknown', 'name': 'Remote upload endpoint not identified', 'description': 'The RCA refers to a remote upload endpoint involved in the outbound VerifySrc transfer, but the endpoint identity is unknown from the available evidence.'}, {'id': 'gap_specific_abort_trigger_unconfirmed', 'name': 'Specific abort trigger unconfirmed', 'description': 'The RCA has medium confidence on the specific abort trigger because available evidence does not distinguish conclusively between remote endpoint failure, remote slowness, connection rejection, or an insufficient VerifySrc timeout.'}, {'id': 'gap_commander_host_not_identified', 'name': 'Commander host not identified', 'description': 'The Commander host is not identified in the RCA, and no evidence ties a Commander component to this failure.'}, {'id': 'gap_script_behavior_unconfirmed', 'name': 'VerifySrc script timeout behavior not confirmed', 'description': 'The RCA states the VerifySrc script may have an insufficient timeout, but this cannot be confirmed without the step logs or script-level evidence.'}]",
