ion\":\"Procedure included the failed VerifySrc step.\",\"source_id\":\"procedure_Build_Rel_602829\",\"target_id\":\"step_f179cca2_24b5_f148_8b4a_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_step_instance_of_stepclass\",\"name\":\"instance_of\",\"description\":\"The failed step is an execution instance of the VerifySrc source verification step class.\",\"source_id\":\"step_f179cca2_24b5_f148_8b4a_4efb9ff91010\",\"target_id\":\"step_class_VerifySrc\"},{\"id\":\"rel_step_has_build_symptom\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"VerifySrc failure led to the CloudBees completed_error Compile classification.\",\"source_id\":\"step_f179cca2_24b5_f148_8b4a_4efb9ff91010\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_build_completed_error_compile\"},{\"id\":\"rel_step_has_exit0_symptom\",\"name\":\"has_symptom\",\"description\":\"VerifySrc failed even though the process exit code was 0.\",\"source_id\":\"step_f179cca2_24b5_f148_8b4a_4efb9ff91010\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_VerifySrc_failed_exit_0\"},{\"id\":\"rel_cifs_active_during_step\",\"name\":\"active_during\",\"description\":\"QCDFS CIFS authentication errors were active during the entire VerifySrc execution window.\",\"source_id\":\"symptom_QCDFS_errors_during_VerifySrc\",\"target_id\":\"step_f179cca2_24b5_f148_8b4a_4efb9ff91010\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rootcause_causes_cifs\",\"name\":\"causes\",\"description\":\"Farm-wide Kerberos expiry caused CIFS/SMB session setup authentication failures against QCDFS.\",\"source_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_CIFS_SessSetup_EACCES\"},{\"id\":\"rel_rootcause_causes_build_failure\",\"name\":\"causes\",\"description\":\"QCDFS authentication failure caused VerifySrc source access failure and downstream build completed_error Compile classification.\",\"source_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_build_completed_error_compile\"},{\"id\":\"rel_key_expiry_supports_rootcause\",\"name\":\"supports\",\"description\":\"The explicit [Errno 127] Key has expired log supports the Kerberos expiry root cause mechanism.\",\"source_id\":\"symptom_Kerberos_key_expired\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_farm_status_supports_rootcause\",\"name\":\"supports\",\"description\":\"The farm-wide impact across 19 hosts supports a systemic Kerberos/QCDFS authentication issue.\",\"source_id\":\"status_farm_wide_impact\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_outage_status_supports_rootcause\",\"name\":\"supports\",\"description\":\"The sustained QCDFS Kerberos outage status supports the root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"status_QCDFS_Kerberos_outage\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_crossjob_supports_rootcause\",\"name\":\"supports\",\"description\":\"Identical failure pattern in another job supports the systemic root cause.\",\"source_id\":\"symptom_cross_job_same_pattern\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_gap_no_dd_limits_confidence\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"No Datadog telemetry on crm-ubuntulv118 limits direct confirmation on the failing agent.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_no_datadog_telemetry_crm_ubuntulv118\",\"target_id\":\"annotation_confidence_medium_high\"},{\"id\":\"rel_gap_no_direct_limits_confidence\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"Kerberos expiry was not directly observed on crm-ubuntulv118, limiting confidence.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_no_direct_kerberos_expiry_on_crm_ubuntulv118\",\"target_id\":\"annotation_confidence_medium_high\"},{\"id\":\"rel_gap_cb_logs_limits_confidence\",\"name\":\"limits_confidence\",\"description\":\"Unavailable CloudBees step logs from crm-ubuntulv118 limit definitive confirmation.\",\"source_id\":\"gap_cloudbees_step_logs_unavailable\",\"target_id\":\"annotation_confidence_medium_high\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remed_renew_addresses_rootcause\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Renewing Kerberos credentials addresses the identified root cause mechanism.\",\"source_id\":\"remediation_renew_kerberos_credentials\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remed_verify_addresses_symptom\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Verifying QCDFS mount accessibility confirms recovery from CIFS authentication failures.\",\"source_id\":\"remediation_verify_QCDFS_mount_accessibility\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_CIFS_SessSetup_EACCES\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remed_rerun_addresses_build_failure\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Re-running failed jobs addresses the build failures after QCDFS access is restored.\",\"source_id\":\"remediation_rerun_failed_jobs\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_build_completed_error_compile\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remed_audit_addresses_crossjob\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Auditing outage-window jobs addresses potential additional failures caused by the same outage.\",\"source_id\":\"remediation_audit_jobs_during_outage\",\"target_id\":\"status_QCDFS_Kerberos_outage\"},{\"id\":\"rel_remed_install_dd_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Installing Datadog agents addresses missing telemetry coverage on uncovered hosts.\",\"source_id\":\"remediation_install_datadog_agent_missing_hosts\",\"target_id\":\"gap_no_datadog_telemetry_crm_ubuntulv118\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prev_renewal_prevents_rootcause\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"Automated ticket renewal is intended to prevent future Kerberos ticket expiry outages.\",\"source_id\":\"preventive_automated_kerberos_ticket_renewal\",\"target_id\":\"root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prev_qcdfs_monitor_detects_cifs\",\"name\":\"detects\",\"description\":\"QCDFS mount health monitor detects CIFS SessSetup = -13 error cascades.\",\"source_id\":\"preventive_QCDFS_mount_health_monitor\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_CIFS_SessSetup_EACCES\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prev_key_monitor_detects_key_expiry\",\"name\":\"detects\",\"description\":\"Kerberos key expiry monitor detects [Errno 127] Key has expired on QCDFS paths.\",\"source_id\":\"preventive_Kerberos_key_expiry_monitor\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_Kerberos_key_expired\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prev_preflight_prevents_generic_failure\",\"name\":\"prevents\",\"description\":\"VerifySrc pre-flight QCDFS check prevents opaque Compile failures by failing fast with actionable QCDFS/Kerberos errors.\",\"source_id\":\"preventive_VerifySrc_preflight_QCDFS_check\",\"target_id\":\"symptom_build_completed_error_compile\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prev_incident_addresses_no_incident\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Auto-incident creation addresses lack of formal incident declaration for farm-wide outages.\",\"source_id\":\"preventive_auto_incident_for_farm_outages\",\"target_id\":\"status_no_formal_incident\"},{\"id\":\"rel_prev_dd_agents_addresses_gap\",\"name\":\"addresses\",\"description\":\"Datadog deployment across all CRMBuilds agents addresses future telemetry gaps.\",\"source_id\":\"preventive_Datadog_agents_all_CRMBuilds_agents\",\"target_id\":\"gap_no_datadog_telemetry_crm_ubuntulv118\"}]}",
    "embedding_text": "Log symptoms:  [{'id': 'symptom_build_completed_error_compile', 'name': 'CloudBees job completed_error with Compile classification', 'description': 'Job f179cca2-18f5-f1a4-9b68-4efb9ff91010 ended at 2026-07-07T06:33:42Z with status completed_error / error and failed reason Compile.'}, {'id': 'symptom_VerifySrc_failed_exit_0', 'name': 'VerifySrc failed despite exit code 0', 'description': 'VerifySrc process exited cleanly with code 0, indicating the failure was detected by step verification logic rather than an OS-level crash.'}, {'id': 'symptom_CIFS_SessSetup_EACCES', 'name': 'CIFS VFS SessSetup = -13 EACCES errors', 'description': 'Datadog logs recorded 50,676+ CIFS SessSetup = -13 errors targeting \\\\\\\\QCDFS.qualcomm.com from at least 2026-07-07T06:00:00Z through 2026-07-07T07:29:59Z across 19 build hosts, at approximately 560 errors per minute.'}, {'id': 'symptom_Kerberos_key_expired', 'name': 'Kerberos key expired on QCDFS mount', 'description': \"Datadog log on host lpi-aci-ubld040 at 2026-07-07T06:34:58Z reported [Errno 127] Key has expired: '/mnt/qcdfs/adas/SE03/DataLake/DCS02' while ansible-ansible.builtin.find attempted to access the QCDFS mount.\"}, {'id': 'symptom_QCDFS_errors_during_VerifySrc', 'name': 'QCDFS authentication errors active during VerifySrc window', 'description': 'During the VerifySrc window, Datadog per-minute analysis showed CIFS errors continuing: 564 at 06:27Z, 566 at 06:28Z, 566 at 06:29Z, and 570 at 06:30Z.'}, {'id': 'symptom_cross_job_same_pattern', 'name': 'Second job failed with identical pattern', 'description': 'RCA states that job f179cd8b, Aurora.LA.3.1-00150-STD.PROD-2, failed in the same window with the same procedure, same step, and same exit code, supporting a systemic failure pattern.'}]\n    \n Root Causes:  [{'id': 'root_cause_farm_wide_Kerberos_ticket_expiry_QCDFS_auth_failure', 'name': 'Farm-wide Kerberos ticket expiry causing QCDFS CIFS authentication failure', 'description': 'The VerifySrc step failed because the build agent could not authenticate to \\\\\\\\QCDFS.qualcomm.com over CIFS/SMB to access source files. Linux CIFS returned -13 EACCES during SMB session setup. The mechanism is supported by explicit [Errno 127] Key has expired evidence on a QCDFS mount and by sustained farm-wide CIFS SessSetup errors.'}]\n    \n Data Gaps:  [{'id': 'gap_no_datadog_telemetry_crm_ubuntulv118', 'name': 'No Datadog telemetry for crm-ubuntulv118', 'description': 'Agent host crm-ubuntulv118 was not registered in Datadog infrastructure inventory. No CPU, memory, disk, network metrics, or logs were available from this specific host.'}, {'id': 'gap_no_direct_kerberos_expiry_on_crm_ubuntulv118', 'name': 'Kerberos expiry not directly observed on failing agent', 'description': 'The explicit [Errno 127] Key has expired log was observed on lpi-aci-ubld040, not on crm-ubuntulv118. RCA infers consistency for crm-ubuntulv118 from farm-wide evidence and timing.'}, {'id': 'gap_cloudbees_step_logs_unavailable', 'name': 'CloudBees step execution logs from crm-ubuntulv118 unavailable', 'description': 'RCA states CloudBees step execution logs from crm-ubuntulv118 must be examined directly for definitive confirmation, but they were not available in the investigation.'}, {'id': 'gap_commander_host_not_identified', 'name': 'Commander host not identified', 'description': 'Execution path inventory states the Commander host was not identified, though there was no evidence of Commander contribution to the failure.'}, {'id': 'gap_exact_kerberos_failure_mode_unresolved', 'name': 'Exact Kerberos renewal failure mode unresolved', 'description': 'RCA identifies either farm-wide Kerberos keytab/TGT expiry or KDC unreachability preventing renewal as possible underlying mechanisms; the exact one is not proven.'}, {'id': 'gap_splunk_not_queried', 'name': 'Splunk not queried', 'description': 'RCA states Splunk was not queried because Datadog flex logs were considered sufficient and conclusive for this investigation.'}]",
